^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I admit, with DONT it is hard to get into the auction with a single suited minor, but if playing DONT you should probably double right away. The basic principle here is you should get into the auction early, before allowing the opponents to exchange information. Some people like to delay, to "see what is going on", but I do not generally subscribe to that theory.|
