^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now let us discuss the play a bit.  noi knows I have 4 hearts from the auction. Therefore, she should strongly suspect betty has a singleton. Therefore, she should play the ace on the first trick, otherwise, betty is going to get some ruffs, as she did.|
