NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The important principle here, which many less experienced players don't follow, is that the auction often gives you lots of clues as to what is going on. You need to remember the auction, and take advantage of all the available clues. In this case, the heart suit was an open book to noi.|
