NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The only other issue was my suit preference. As most of you know, the size of my heart, which I know betty is ruffing, tells betty which suit to lead back. A low heart by me says lead the lower of the two non-trump suits (clubs), a high heart says lead the higher of the 2 suits (spades). Since I led the 3, it told betty to lead clubs.|
